        },
        {
            "id": 6308756,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 穩懋(3105)股價殺至跌停，跌停價210.0元，成交29,317張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>穩懋(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3105:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3105\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3105-TW</a>)13日10:21下跌23元，股價跌停報210.0元，委買1,637,000張、委賣2,000張，成交29,317張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為電子零組件製造業。電子材料批發業。除許可業務外,得經營法令非禁止或限制之業務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>穩懋(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3105:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3105\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3105-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲27.32%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲3.96%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+10,605 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+6,200 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+2,283 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+2,122 張</li> <li>融資增減：+9,649 張</li> <li>融券增減：+1,124 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
